Please, somebody.

Yes, this post is to bump the tread up, but if I don't do this, nobody will help me. Please, download the link a look wha's wrong. I don't want all my work is for nothing.

Well, for starters, you are going to want to change the line

name = fuelTank

if you're trying to create a NEW part. Right now it has the same parameter as the default tank. The folder name is irrelevant and only affects how it's sorted in the VAB. To create a new part, you have to give it an original name.

That's all I see that might be an issue.

Cheers!
